properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - CHATSWOOD Railway Street between Day Street AND Help Street
properties.otherAdvice:
Special event clearways will be in effect to facilitate rail replacement bus operations for Sydney Metro trackwork. No-stopping zones will also be in place on the western side of Railway St between Help St and Brown St during this time. 

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
